<h2 id="configure-tools-with-good-defaults">6. Configure tools with good defaults</h2>
<p>DDS does not prescribe tools. However, because tool defaults are not automatically compliant, teams must:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Override default colours and typography to align with DDS.</li>
  <li>Test accessibility within the actual tool environment.</li>
  <li>If a tool cannot meet requirements, provide an alternative.</li>
  <li>Consider accessibility capability when selecting vendors.</li>
</ul>


